      "content": "```python\ndef calculate_final_price(order):\n    subtotal = order['subtotal']\n    region = order['region']\n    item_category = order['item_category']\n    discount_code = order['discount_code']\n\n    # Apply discount if applicable\n    if discount_code == 'SAVE10':\n        subtotal *= 0.9\n\n    # Calculate VAT and luxury taxes based on region and item category\n    if region == 'UK':\n        vat = 0.20\n        luxury_tax = 0.05 if item_category == 'luxury' else 0.0\n    elif region == 'DE':\n        vat = 0.19\n        luxury_tax = 0.0\n    elif region == 'FR':\n        vat = 0.20\n        luxury_tax = 0.10\n    else:\n        raise ValueError(\"Unsupported region\")\n\n    final_price = subtotal * (1 + vat) + subtotal * luxury_tax\n    return final_price\n\ndef test_pricing():\n    # Test 1: UK Standard\n    order1 = {'region': 'UK', 'subtotal': 100.0, 'item_category': 'standard', 'discount_code': None}\n    assert calculate_final_price(order1)",
